title: Darkened Skye Playthrough — Part 1
description: So I played this game as a kid and really never got that far in it at all. I remember thinking it was funny and I liked the fact that it had skittles in it. Well, now I'm playing it again, and holy shit is it an unbelievably stupid/bizarre game. I mean, it's not shitty to play, it's fairly enjoyable, but the story and the dialogue in the game is just so cringey it's insane. This game is definitely going to be an experience. I am planning on speedrunning it too... so that'll be fun.
